  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Before you start cooking, take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air, then boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely slice your<strong> brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>stock</strong> <strong>mix</strong> in 225ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[300ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[450ml]</span> <strong>boiled</strong> <strong>water</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1699030413330-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
