      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>cider</strong> <strong>vinegar</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> in a bowl – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>baby</strong> <strong>leaf</strong> <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>baby leaf salad</strong> to the bowl with the <strong>dressing</strong> and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>dressed salad</strong></p>",
