    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>baharat chicken stew</strong> over the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>rice</strong> with the <strong>dressed</strong> <strong>salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Scatter the <strong>pomegranate</strong> <strong>seeds</strong> all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
